parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission problems can cause the vehicle to lose power, jerk, or hesitate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Lack of power
gears not engaging or delayed engagement
jerking or hesitation
transmission slipping
RPMs racing
and inability to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter button can cause the vehicle to shift into neutral or reverse while driving, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Button on gear shift selector sticks or breaks
preventing the key from being removed
and allowing the shifter to move freely between gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system problems can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Key gets stuck in the ignition
electrical system refuses to chime when keys are left in ignition
locks lock and unlock randomly
and lights flicker.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cooling system problems can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: Engine smells of overheated radiator and coolant
engine overheats
and radiator hose needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Other issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction or become unsafe to operate.
symptoms: Traction control light and check engine light come on
vehicle goes into limp mode
and vehicle stalls or dies.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shift button can cause the vehicle to shift out of park without pressing the brake, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The gear shift button sticks
the key refuses to come out
the vehicle shifts from park to drive without stepping on the brake
the button breaks
and the vehicle is unable to shift out of drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, stalling, or even fires.
symptoms: Coolant leaks
cracked coolant reservoir
broken water outlet
overheating engine
and engine stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes do not work properly
the vehicle does not slow down
and the brake pedal feels smooth.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Misfire and Air Vent Tube Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine misfire and air vent tube issues can cause the check engine light to come on, leading to engine damage or stalling.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
engine misfire
and cracked air vent tube.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the warning chime can cause the driver to be unaware of important safety warnings, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The warning chime does not sound for certain warnings
such as overheating or tire pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabiltrak system and engine issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The Stabiltrak light comes on
engine stalling
and high RPMs when shifting into park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaks and flooding can cause electrical system failures, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: Water leaks into the passenger compartment
flooding
and faulty manufacturing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death to the passenger.
symptoms: The passenger airbag "off" light remains illuminated even when a passenger is in the seat
the airbag light flickers on and off
the airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag sensor is faulty
and the airbag warning indicator is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning indicator can indicate a faulty airbag system, which can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator is illuminated
the airbag light flickers on and off
the airbag sensor is faulty
and the passenger airbag "off" light remains illuminated even when a passenger is in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death to the occupants.
symptoms: The airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag sensor is faulty
and the airbag warning indicator is illuminated.
